(nICacheTLBWays, power_internal).explanation: Increasing the number of TLB ways requires more hardware structures and logic circuits, which directly increases internal power consumption due to additional transistors and switching activity;

(nICacheTLBWays, area_net_area).explanation: More TLB ways require additional routing and interconnect structures to connect the extra hardware components, directly increasing the net area occupied by wiring;

(nICacheTLBWays, nDCacheTLBWays).explanation: The number of instruction cache TLB ways and data cache TLB ways are independent design parameters that can be configured separately without direct causal relationship;
